{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bb950f141a","title":"“青年人的前途在官僚主义者手中”","origin":"北京地质勘探学院党委会宣传部编《社会主义教育参考资料第二编：右派言论汇编》，1957年10月5日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"831facfd6b","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"bb950f141a"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"7763649f73","name":"高明球"},{"id":"82cc012e26","name":"北京地质勘探学院"},{"id":"834a343216","name":"张风翔"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"428d839a2d","type":"title","text":"“青年人的前途在官僚主义者手中”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bb950f141a"},{"id":"7309d2ce20","type":"authors","text":"北京地质勘探学院张风翔高明球","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bb950f141a"},{"id":"5082b2ca6a","type":"paragraph","text":"张风翔说：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bb950f141a"},{"id":"f297ca4168","type":"paragraph","text":"「青年人的前途和生命，都掌握在领导者——官僚主义者手中。」","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bb950f141a"},{"id":"b9c37b7c91","type":"paragraph","text":"高明球说:","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bb950f141a"},{"id":"85cb45a603","type":"paragraph","text":"「我妹妹没上大学，都是官僚主义造成的，因为我妹妹参了军，当时本来用不着这么多人，为什么叫她去呢？……。我热爱党，但是，你们年青，经历少，三年前我和你们认识一样，现在我则不那么想了。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bb950f141a"},{"id":"99c1ba9aeb","type":"paragraph","text":"「如我弟弟有一同学，原来认为现实的一切都是美好的，可是后来他也成为反对派。对观实，譬如一张纸远看是白纸，近看却有许多斑点，要说是白纸，只好远处看。」","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bb950f141a"}],"page":{"id":"b2273fa6b3","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bb950f141a","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}